text: Jim Henry (born 8 April 1947) is a Canadian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Canada Category:Equestrians at the 1975 Pan American Games Category:Sportspeople from Toronto
